{"tid":2057734,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人個另一半成日都話攰?","createTime":"2020-06-09T15:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T04:31:07.000Z","uid":233862,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"439a143fd0abf786eb669bd3f312bf79a6517afb","tid":2057734,"uid":233862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:18:20.000Z","msg":"返工正常9-6 <br />\n朝早成日聽唔到鬧鐘遲到<br />\n放工食完飯就訓 咩都做唔到 <br />\n佢話自己體能差 想做返多啲運動<br />\n但就連我建議佢食完飯唔好即刻上床訓 可以企下行下 <br />\n佢都唔肯做<br />\n星期六日又訓到2點 邊度都無動力去 最多出去行下食飯 <br />\n想同佢行下山去遠啲玩根本無可能<br />\n其實人人都要返工 攰係正常 但到依個地步 會唔會太誇張"},{"pid":"01c5928d917fa9954034b2b2920754d8a4b75302","tid":2057734,"uid":168366,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:19:48.000Z","msg":"返工正常9-6<br />\n<br />\nfact checked?"},{"pid":"eb06ca597c1e36e3f4309ebb761ed09069e7895e","tid":2057734,"uid":233862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01c5928d917fa9954034b2b2920754d8a4b75302","tid":2057734,"uid":168366,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:19:48.000Z","msg":"返工正常9-6<br />\n<br />\nfact checked?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:20:16.000Z","msg":"係 放工就返屋企"},{"pid":"e8c34d167b19ed55f304530d6b0c4d8344582123","tid":2057734,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:20:53.000Z","msg":"做得多咪攰囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a562464e4bc960680daa7018e626e199343f2f","tid":2057734,"uid":233862,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8c34d167b19ed55f304530d6b0c4d8344582123","tid":2057734,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:20:53.000Z","msg":"做得多咪攰囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:21:56.000Z","msg":"依個問題都傾過 因為次數越嚟越少 佢就係話返工太攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943c7cd4e75ee6aa030d932cc707ead737e48714","tid":2057734,"uid":200305,"like